Food Order App:

Extend development of existing app with real data of one neighborhood
User is able to decide what food to order from available restaurants.  User is able to start selection with category, cuisine, or a restaurant.  
All users needs to create an account with the system to be able to use it.
Admin users can manage the data — add, edit, delete users, restaurants, restaurant menus, categories of food, cuisines etc.
May incorporate food item nutrition information so that user can select an informed choice.


